  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC451">
        <l>muṉṉilai muṉṉa rīyu mēyu</l>
	<l>mannilai marapiṉ meyyūrntu varumē.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/250/mode/1up">250</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/250/mode/1up">250</ref>.</p>
<p>ic cūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, iṭaiccollōttiṉuḷ oḻintu niṉṟa oḻipu uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>urai : muṉṉilaikkaṇṇāṉa īkāra ēkāra iṭaic coṟkaḷ muṉṉilaikkup poruntiya meyyai yūrntu varum eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>varalāṟu :</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC451-Iḷam-cit1">
<l>'ceṉṟī perumaniṟ ṟakaikkunar yārē'</l>	<p>[akam - 46]</p></lg>
<p>eṉavum,</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC451-Iḷam-cit2">
<l>'aṭṭi lōlai toṭṭaṉai niṉmē'</l>	<p>[naṟṟiṇai - 300]</p></lg>
<p>eṉavum, ivai yiraṇṭum tattaṅ kuṟippiṟ poruḷ ceyyum iṭaiccol eṉpatu ; īṇṭu epporuḷai viḷakki niṉṟaṉavō eṉiṉ, puṟattuṟavu nīrmaip poruḷpaṭa vanta eṉṟavāṟu.	(55)</p>

 </body>
  </text>

